text: Malyye Karkaly () is a rural locality (a selo) in Bolshekarkalinksy Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 196 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 34 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 5 km from Bolshiye Karkaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Malyye Karkaly
